\cf0 \ul \ulc0 FDTK Package Contents\ulnone \
\
- bin/\
	as2api/	- open source as2 documentation tool: packaged with ruby, windows and osx executables\
	mtasc/		- open source as2 compiler: packaged latest builds for windows and os x\
	scripts/	- scripts to automate common tasks; documentation, ssh+rysnc etc.\
\
- doc/			- various usage documents (FTD/Eclipse shortcuts, etc.)\
\
- lib/\
	FP7/		- complete core library for Flash 7\
	FP8/		- complete core library for Flash 8\
	FP9/		- complete core library for Flash 9\
	templates/	- useful collection of FDT templates\
